statement:
\emph{Multiple Choice question: Select ONE correct answer. You will not
be graded for any work.}

For which of these differential equations is \emph{y = 3} a steady state
solution?

(a) \emph{dy/dt = 2y-6}

(b) \emph{dy/dt = y\textsuperscript{2}+9}

(c) \emph{dy/dt = 1/(3-y)}

(d) \emph{dy/dt = cos($\pi$y)}

(e) \emph{dy/dt = 3}
